                    <div class="common-banner-title">
                        <img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/azure-firewall_icon@2x.svg" />
                        <h2>Azure 防火墙<span>Azure Firewall</span></h2>
                        <h4>云和本地网络安全，用于保护 Azure 虚拟网络资源</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_mysql_trial">申请试用<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em>
